title: Was Cesar Seok a pro-Obama stripper before Trump climbed?
subtitle: Cesar Seok Jr., the alleged anti-democratic postal bomber, was naked at different stages of his life, but there was no evidence that he had expressed any views in favour of Obama.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Cesar Sayuk, the man accused of sending bombs to senior democratic legislators and critical media organizations of President Trump, was a stripper and was "long known for Obama's support."
